Class Facet.DateRangeFacet.DateMathRangeFacet<T extends DateMathExpression>

    T - Spectated type of content from the field to be faceted.
    Enclosing class:
    Facet.DateRangeFacet<T>

    public static class Facet.DateRangeFacet.DateMathRangeFacet<T extends DateMathExpression>
extends Facet.DateRangeFacet
    Class which allows to perform ranged facet query on a DateMathExpression typed date field. A facet ranged query returns all the documents which have the specified field with a value included in a range defined by Facet.DateRangeFacet.start and Facet.DateRangeFacet.end. The result documents are faceted in the range steps of the size described by the property Facet.DateRangeFacet.gap.

        name - String with a custom name for the instance of the facet. It should be alphanumeric.
        fieldDescriptor - FieldDescriptor to do the range query on. T must extend Date.
        start - T Starting value of the defined range. T must extend DateMathExpression.
        end - T Ending value of the defined range. T must extend DateMathExpression.
        gap - Long Size of the steps in which the range is divided to facet the results.
        timeUnit - TimeUnit Units in which the gap is given.
        pivotNames - Name of the pivots using this facet.
